&lt;h4&gt;The bad...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Kennedy Center closing after Trump&#39;s failed takeover &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2026/feb/01/kennedy-center-dc-closed-trump&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
