&lt;section&gt;
    &lt;p class=&quot;tangerine&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center;font-size:4em;padding:1.2rem 0px;&quot;&gt;Impeach. Convict. Remove.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Recap of this week in the revolution: Nationwide protests demand ICE out of our cities. Trump regime targets journalists to silence free press. FBI seizes 2020 voter records in Georgia. Another (partial) government shutdown begins.&lt;/p&gt;
