&lt;section class=&quot;block the-ugly&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The ugly...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Feds raid GA election office and seize 2020 voter records &lt;a href=&quot;https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/fbi-conducting-court-ordered-activity-georgia-election-site/story?id=129644345&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;

    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/DscHPA_4BV-640.webp&quot; class=&quot;lightbox-link&quot; aria-haspopup=&quot;dialog&quot; style=&quot;cursor:zoom-in&quot;&gt;
      &lt;img class=&quot;img-lightbox&quot; alt=&quot;Fulton County Elections Hub and Operation Center&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/DscHPA_4BV-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; height=&quot;640&quot; srcset=&quot;/images/DscHPA_4BV-200.webp 200w, /images/DscHPA_4BV-640.webp 640w&quot; sizes=&quot;200px&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;

        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;FBI agents carted off pallets of official 2020 voter records from Fulton County, Georgia. The seizure was ordered by the Trump regime based on Donny 2-Dolls&#39; repeatedly-disproven claims that he won the 2020 presidential election. Fulton County officials have expressed deep concern about the FBI&#39;s seizure. The records are the original voter records from the election that have been protected by Fulton County since 2020. Now that they have been seized by agents of the federal government, there is no longer a public chain of custody. Nobody knows where the records are being taken or who is protecting them. Now that the chain of custody has been broken, any &quot;conclusions&quot; that can be drawn from these ballots is unreliable at best because there is no way to prove that these records have not been tampered with.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The results of the 2020 election have been held up repeatedly throughout multiple investigations, and there is absolutely no sign of any wrongdoing&amp;mdash;with one exception: Donny 2-Dolls called election officials in Fulton County after he lost the election and asked them to &quot;find&quot; him enough votes to overturn the results of the election and threatened to press charges against Secretary of State Brad Raffensperger if he refused to comply.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The simple fact is that Trump lost the 2020 election fair and square. And even if he feels like he should have won, it&#39;s completely irrelevant because he is currently the President of the United States of America. So even if his outrageous lies could be shown to be true, it would not do or change anything in the world&amp;mdash;he&#39;d still be the president. So what&#39;s the point?&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The point is that the Trump regime is setting the stage to either rig, undermine, or eliminate the 2026 mid-term elections. The first year of his second term in office has been an unmitigated disaster from the very beginning. His approval ratings are abysmal, his own base is starting to question his actions, his mental health is rapidly deteriorating, and he is afraid. There is little doubt that if the Republicans lose their majority in Congress, Trump will be impeached and there is actually a slim chance he will be removed from office. He&#39;s doing everything he can to prevent that from happening.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;What does this have to do with Fulton? Now that the Trump regime has captured the voter records from 2020, they will alter the results, claim that the election was, indeed, rigged or stolen, and then claim that the fraud was perpetrated through mail-in ballots. He will then try to prevent states from allowing mail-in ballots in the 2026 elections. This will make it harder for many voters to cast their vote, and history seems to indicate that elections with lower voter turnouts tend to favor the Republican Party.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
