&lt;section class=&quot;block info&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Keeping you informed...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Another government shutdown &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/ce8rk33dpvmo?at_medium=RSS&amp;at_campaign=rss&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;

    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/aSZVN262v9-800.webp&quot; class=&quot;lightbox-link&quot; aria-haspopup=&quot;dialog&quot; style=&quot;cursor:zoom-in&quot;&gt;
      &lt;img class=&quot;img-lightbox&quot; alt=&quot;U.S. House of Representatives&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/aSZVN262v9-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;419&quot; srcset=&quot;/images/aSZVN262v9-200.webp 200w, /images/aSZVN262v9-800.webp 800w&quot; sizes=&quot;200px&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;

            &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;United States House of Representatives&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Just 11 weeks after the end of the last government shutdown, the US government is once again shut down. This shutdown is technically only a partial shutdown because Senators approved a funding bill to approve funding for most government departments through September, but only provides 2 weeks of funding for the Department of Homeland Security, which provides funding for ICE. The Senate bill still has to be approved by the House of Representatives, which was not in session last week and is likely to vote on the bill early next week.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The bill approves continued funding for DHS for 2 weeks to give Congress a chance to come to an agreement on future funding for ICE. Despite the public demands to abolish ICE completely, Democrats are only asking for promises of new rules and the requirement of oversight and judicial warrants for ICE activities. They want ICE agents to operate without masks, wear and use body cameras, and wear visible identification.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;This shutdown does not affect food assistance programs or the VA, which have already been funded through the end of the fiscal year in September. &lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
