	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Reporter reveals the sloppy ICE-stapo recruitment process &lt;a href=&quot;https://slate.com/news-and-politics/2026/01/ice-recruitment-minneapolis-shooting.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
