        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;While the Trump regime is actively engaged in rounding up and deporting hard-working immigrants and imposing ridiculous requirements on tourists entering the country, they are also making it clear that this level of persecution only applies to the poor. If you&#39;re rich enough, you can literally buy a golden ticket to gain access to everything the United States has to offer. The ticket entitles its owner to permanent legal residency in the United States and a streamlined path to citizenship.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Donny 2-Dolls said the program will result in &quot;somebody great coming into our country because we think these will be some tremendous people.&quot; This tells you everything you need to know about our current Idiot in Chief. According to him, having money automatically makes a person &quot;tremendous,&quot; while poor people are expendable at best, and a nuisance to be eradicated at worst.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;When the idea was first released back in March, the Trump regime priced the cards at $5 million and estimated they would sell hundreds of thousands of the cards, raking in at least a trillion dollars. They&#39;ve lowered the price to a paltry $1 million, but are still expecting to earn billions of dollars from the program. And what do they plan to do with all this money they are going to be raking in? Donny 2-Dolls says the payments for these golden tickets will &quot;go to the U.S. government...where we can do things positive for the country.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
