	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Admiral Holsey set to retire early amid tension over Caribbean strikes &lt;a href=&quot;https://allaboutlawyer.com/admiral-alvin-holsey-retires-friday-after-clash-with-hegseth-over-venezuela-strikes/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
