        James Comey and Letitia James cases dropped (for now) &lt;a href=&quot;https://apnews.com/article/comey-james-justice-department-5ec1a59d152bc1fd000ade15e20745b5&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
