    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Trump&#39;s handpicked attorney mishandles Comey case &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.commondreams.org/news/comey-case-tainted-halligan&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
