        Democrats hand yet another victory to Trump regime &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/11/10/us-senate-nears-vote-on-bill-to-end-40-day-government-shutdown&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
