&lt;p&gt;Recap of this week in the revolution: Encouraging election results and jury finds &amp;quot;Sandwich Guy&amp;quot; not guilty of assaulting a federal officer. Government shutdowns breaks records for longest in history. Trump flaunts his wealth while SNAP benefits expire for the poorest. What is democratic socialism?&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;section class=&quot;block the-good&quot;&gt;
	&lt;h4&gt;The good...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Encouraging results from key elections nationwide &lt;a href=&quot;https://apps.npr.org/2025-election-results/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
