		&lt;ol&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;New York City Mayor: &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zohran_Mamdani&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Zohran Mamdani&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
