    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Assault with a sandwich? Nah. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.usatoday.com/picture-gallery/news/nation/2025/11/06/sandwich-guy-not-guilty-assault-federal-officer-cultural-moment/87132759007/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
