&lt;section class=&quot;block info&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Keeping you informed...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        What is Democratic Socialism? &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npr.org/2025/11/05/nx-s1-5599928/democratic-socialism-explained-zohran-mamdani-bernie-sanders&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;
            &lt;img class=&quot;img-link&quot; alt=&quot;Fist and Rose&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/j3es34HgMu-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;290&quot;&gt;
            &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;The Fist and Rose: A common symbol of democratic socialism. Image by &lt;a href=&quot;https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:RootOfAllLight&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;RoofOfAllLight&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=&quot;https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Pu%C3%B1o_y_rosa.svg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Wikimedia Commons.&lt;/a&gt; Licensed under the &lt;a href=&quot;https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/deed.en&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Creative Commons  CC0 1.0 Universal Public Domain Dedication license&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;The next mayor of New York City is a self-proclaimed Democratic Socialist. So is Senator Bernie Sanders. And Representative Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez. But what does it mean to be a democratic socialist?&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;The simple truth is that, like most political ideologies, there is no single, absolute, definitive definition of the term. There&#39;s lots of room for interpretation and disagreement even among people who identify with the label. Broadly speaking, democratic socialists believe that certain sectors of the economy (such as healthcare, housing, and transportation) cannot provide the public benefit necessary if they are run solely for profit.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;The primary purpose of democratic socialism is to curb capitalism&#39;s excesses through progressive reforms that target human rights and dignity over profitability.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npr.org/2025/11/05/nx-s1-5599928/democratic-socialism-explained-zohran-mamdani-bernie-sanders&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(NPR) NYC&#39;s next mayor is a democratic socialist. What does that mean?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Democratic_socialism&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(Wikipedia) Democratic socialism&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
