	&lt;h4&gt;The good...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Senate passes resolution to undo Trump regime tariffs &lt;a href=&quot;https://apnews.com/article/congress-trump-tariffs-china-525d652549af2fbe2931fa57aeaa32e6&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
