                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://apnews.com/article/trinidad-warship-trump-venezuela-5aba7cf99e78a050556c4ddccc2e6e96&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(AP) US warship docks in Trinidad and Tobago, putting more pressure on Venezuela&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.democracynow.org/2025/10/27/headlines/venezuela_denounces_the_us_for_docking_warship_in_trinidad_and_tobago&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(Democracy Now) Venezuela denounces the U.S. for docking warship in Trinidad and Tobago&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
